{"tid":1315135,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直到比錢升級左<<蘋果日報>>會員才夢醒，其實它是垃圾","createTime":"2019-07-14T12:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T17:31:55.000Z","uid":81028,"like":9,"dislike":327,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e2f6abcaaba7901c695f23d7d19b4dec97216d","tid":1315135,"uid":81028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>直到比錢升級左&lt;&lt;蘋果日報&gt;&gt;會員才夢醒，其實它是垃圾</strong><br />\n<br />\n細細個開始睇毒&lt;&lt;蘋果&gt;&gt;,睇左好多年，最近開始玩收費，$3 玩2個月就試下啦。<br />\n比完錢才是噩夢的開始：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 蘋果動新聞（香港）不會儲存你的信用卡資料:</strong><br />\n佢個官網寫到明話唔會儲存你的信用卡資料, 但我比完錢在會員中就會發現佢地儲存左我的信用卡資料而且<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無法移除</span></strong>！！！！<br />\nAmazon 都可以移除信用卡資料，而蘋果日報係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無得比你移除</span></strong>，你入左就會記錄你一世。<br />\n請問我是不是可以去海關告他們違反商品銷售條例？<br />\n<br />\n有圖為證：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZihOT0h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZihOT0h.png&h=a257d747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZ5dkFj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZ5dkFj.png&h=905e002f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 取消訂閱:</strong><br />\n我不知道我是的對這個訂閱的理解和大家有無不同，比$3玩2個月去到9月1日，因為蘋果寫住話如果在到期前唔取消訂閱，會繼續自動續訂，咁我一買完就按取消訂閱，點知佢地個&ldquo;取消訂閱&rdquo;同世界標準唔同。<br />\n全世界都係你取消訂閱後，你可以繼續使用個服務，直到訂閱期屆滿，而蘋果日報的&ldquo;取消訂閱&rdquo;係一按取消就無左個訂閱資格。無眼睇啦。<br />\n<br />\n請問大家點理解佢個訂閱試玩：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V40Ay0i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV40Ay0i.png&h=d80c9e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8q8T0i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8q8T0i.png&h=a9a28b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後開始反思看了多年的蘋果日報其實是在發災難財，&ldquo;安心偷食&rdquo;時間打響了會員訂閱的第一炮，之後&ldquo;逃犯條例&rdquo;。<br />\n我不知道這個是否道德，但我知道如果比了錢，我會對他們有要求，而不是免費野無得投訴，對新收費平台的安排<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">非常失望</span></strong>。<br />\n再見了，之後只能轉看其他新聞平台多角度看世界。<br />\n<br />\n香港媒體：<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9ygGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=21d618c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9ygGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=545a41f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com&h=1170b0e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9ygGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=24942b46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wenweipo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenweipo.com%2F&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9ygGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=efd5e84c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wenweipo.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2F&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9ygGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=84c1014c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/</a>"},{"pid":"178b19fe7dd5762d963d802b9338f2fab89009d7","tid":1315135,"uid":279000,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"又一個戇鳩 大家咪撚覆佢由個post沉啦"},{"pid":"b89106b44953dcf1ea3e71c3b4b4d7309139501b","tid":1315135,"uid":135922,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"你share 埋啲乜撚嘢媒體？<br />\n<br />\n東方 文匯？<br />\n<br />\n食撚屎啦3毛"},{"pid":"499baeac2053ee6ad18f6cca51d99680401ff042","tid":1315135,"uid":8165,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"仆街 見到你推薦啲link笑撚左出聲<br />\nBlocked"},{"pid":"ff9466579200f05309fedc3af28f54671105b67b","